00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:10,366
Well, it takes a certain determination
to row against the current.

289
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,050
Yes, it does.

290
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:19,402
Ah, Simmons, how are you?

291
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:22,601
- Excuse me.
