(BEEPING SLOWS)

295
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:13,602
(BEEPING STOPS)

296
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,051
More?

297
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:04,607
So how long were you stuck?

298
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:09,607
Not long, in the scheme of things.

299
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,767
Teething problems.
Building's still settling.

300
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:22,800
Still... I hear all the floors
from the first to the 12th

