biological reason supervenes.

314
00:33:20,040 --> 00:33:23,044
But some of the people who live here,
you've seen them,

315
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:25,686
the vanguard of the well-to-do.

316
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:31,250
