to take the moral high ground.

332
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:37,803
- Tell him.
- No.

333
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,524
Go on!

334
00:34:39,640 --> 00:34:42,291
My daughter was interfered with
in the dark.

335
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:44,528
She's certain it was someone from the top.

336
00:34:44,640 --> 00:34:46,529
He was wearing expensive cologne

337
00:34:46,640 --> 00:34:49,041
and stuffed a copy
of the Financial Times in her mouth.

338
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:51,003
We pay the same charges as the top floors.

339
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:52,929
We want our fair share of the power.

340
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:56,522
Now you pull your finger out
or I'll take it above your head!

341
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:58,881
I think you've made your point, Wilder.

342
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:01,287
Hey, wait. Why don't you
just hold on a minute there?

343
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:03,562
Where the bloody hell
do you think you're going?

344
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:05,887
The service lift's out.
I've gotta come up front.

345
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,445
White wine. Thank God.

346
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:09,602
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa. Oi, oi.

347
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:20,846
