to the vice squad.

653
01:05:35,600 --> 01:05:40,367
Look... I don't know anything about it.

654
01:05:41,680 --> 01:05:43,967
I don't know what caused it.

655
01:05:44,680 --> 01:05:46,648
And I didn't do it.

656
01:05:46,760 --> 01:05:50,446
We're on the same level.
That's all that counts now.

657
01:05:50,600 --> 01:05:52,602
At least until all of this blows over.

658
01:05:54,200 --> 01:05:57,283
- (BARKS)
- Restrain that intruder!

659
01:05:57,400 --> 01:06:00,210
There, look.
What we need is a good sturdy chain!

660
01:06:04,760 --> 01:06:06,364
(THUD; DOG HOWLS)

661
01:06:08,840 --> 01:06:13,243
- What are you doing?
- I'm packing to leave. What do you think?

662
01:06:13,360 --> 01:06:17,729
Has anyone actually made
a formal complaint to the owners?

663
01:06:17,840 --> 01:06:19,842
We are the owners.

664
01:06:19,960 --> 01:06:23,806
Pass me that green thing.
Daddy likes to see me in it.

665
01:06:23,920 --> 01:06:27,208
You're not going anywhere. I forbid it.

666
01:06:28,000 --> 01:06:29,047
(ANN GASPS)

667
01:06:40,160 --> 01:06:41,605
Well...

